result.title: Topcoder Single Round Match 651
result.content:
Merhaba, to everybody!

Tomorrow at 20:00 MSK will be held Topcoder SRM 651.

Let's discuss problems after contest!

UPD: If you have trouble with submitting your solution to div 1 easy, please email your solution to talgorithm@topcoder.com with your handle. If you have the same trouble in other problems, please do the same.

UPD2: It turned out that hundreds of people can't submit their solutions due to system trouble. This match will be unrated. We are sorry for the inconvenience.
